# PROJECT BIENA_ENG
# BIENA_ENG is a project focused on developing an beautiful and user-friendly web-site. Aims to provide an engaging and interactive landing page for the clients being prospected.
## Features
- Responsive design for optimal viewing on various devices.
- Interactive elements to enhance user experience.
- Clean and modern aesthetic to attract and retain visitors.
## Technologies Used
The project uses pnpm (pnpm-lock.yaml)
- It's a Next.js application (app/ directory with layout.tsx, page.tsx)
- It uses TypeScript (tsconfig.json)
- It has Tailwind CSS 
## Installation
1. Clone the repository: `git clone 
2. Navigate to the project directory: `cd BIENA_ENG`
3. Open `index.html` in your web browser to view the landing page.
